  "keyFeatures": [
    "Full ros2_control integration with position, velocity, effort, and force control modes",
    "Scaled joint trajectory controller respecting robot speed scaling",
    "Passthrough trajectory controller for on-robot interpolation",
    "Headless mode operation without teach pendant interaction",
    "Automatic speed scaling and safety-stop handling",
    "Built-in MoveIt2 support via ur_moveit_config",
    "Dashboard client for full robot lifecycle management",
    "Calibration extraction tool for accurate TCP pose",
    "Freedrive, Force Mode, and Tool Contact controllers",
    "Compatible with CB3, PolyScope 5, and PolyScope X robots"
  ],
